de.learnlib.algorithms.features.observationtable

Interface ObservationTable.Inconsistency<I,O>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - input symbol type
    O - observation type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractObservationTable.DefaultInconsistency
    Enclosing interface:
    ObservationTable<I,O>

    public static interface ObservationTable.Inconsistency<I,O>
    Representation of an inconsistency in the observation table.

    An inconsistency is represented by two short prefix rows with matching contents, and an input symbol such that the rows indexed by one-letter extensions have differing contents.

    Author:
    Malte Isberner
